Package team_package

Class Team

java.lang.Object
team_package.Team
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, ProjectTeam
public class Team extends Object implements Serializable, ProjectTeam
Represents a team in a project. A team has an ID, a name, and a list of students who are members of the team.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Kilyan Bentchakal
